snippet.title: Ship carrying Gaza aid still in Cyprus
snippet.description:
The ship carrying desperately need food to Gaza was delayed by several days and remains in Cyprus. Meanwhile, a war of words intensified between President Biden and Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu. NBC News' Richard Engel reports.
